== RIFT-Auction-Management ==

Tool to help track sales in Rift's auction house. It also help determine profit based 
on crafting price and auction deposit cost.

The tool also provide a listing of items that needs to be refilled (crafted)

== Getting Started

If Rails is already installed.

just CD into the application's folder and execute a "Bundle install",
this should download all the required dependencies.

Then execute a "Rails s --Rails_env=Prod" to start the server


If rails and/or Ruby isn't installed. Start with http://www.rubyinstaller.org
and install Ruby 1.8.7

Then install Rails :
"gem install rails"
